                  <li><strong>Featured snippet optimization:</strong> Structure your content to directly answer common questions, as voice assistants often pull from featured snippets.</li>
                  <li><strong>Local search focus:</strong> Many voice searches have local intent, so ensure your business listings are complete and accurate.</li>
                </ul>
